text: Stoyko Malov (born 6 June 1943) is a Bulgarian wrestler. He competed in the men's freestyle flyweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Living people Category:Bulgarian male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Bulgaria Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
